name: TPE Body Alignment System Yoga Mat - Gray
description:
The Heathyoga TPE Body Alignment System Yoga Mat Gray is designed for yoga lovers. Made of nonslip material, certified by SGS. Free of latex, PVC, or any other toxic material. Yoga beginners can use the body alignment lines as body movement guidance when practicing yoga. 



Features

6mm thick
72" x 26"
Double-layer
Free of latex, PVC, or any heavy metal




Accessory: Velcro strap + carry strap
